# 🎓 School Management App (Flutter + Firebase)

Welcome to the official repository of the **School Management App**, a robust and responsive mobile application developed using **Flutter** and **Firebase**.

This app is designed to simplify and streamline school administration tasks such as managing students, teachers, and classes — all from a mobile interface. It’s ideal for small to medium-sized institutions looking to digitize their record-keeping and daily operations.

---

## 🚀 Key Features

- 🔐 **Secure Login System** (Firebase Authentication)
- 🧑 **Student Management** – Add, Edit, View & Delete records
- 👩‍🏫 **Teacher Management** – Add, Edit, View & Delete profiles
- 🏫 **Class-wise Organization** – Assign and track students & teachers
- 🔍 **Search Functionality** – Quick and accurate data retrieval
- ☁️ **Realtime Sync with Firebase** – Instant data update and access
- 📱 **User-Friendly Interface** – Clean, intuitive, and modern design

---

## 🧱 Tech Stack

| Technology | Usage |
|------------|--------|
| **Flutter** | App UI and logic |
| **Dart** | Programming language |
| **Firebase Authentication** | User login system |
| **Firebase Realtime Database** | Data storage and sync |
| **Provider** | State management |

